	  <td valign='top' bgcolor='#F2F2F2' glow='false' glowcolor='#FCA92E' type='dynamic'>1) The SSID does not match the SSID of WRS3.</td>
  </tr>
	<tr bgcolor="#DDDDDD">
	  <td valign='top' glow='false' glowcolor='#FCA92E' type='dynamic'>2) The security mode does not match that of WRS3 (e.g., WEP, WPA, WPA2).</td>
